TIMING-6#1 Critical Warning
No common primary clock between related clocks  
The clocks rgmii_rxc and eth_125M_system_clock are related (timed together) but they have no common primary clock. The design could fail in hardware. To find a timing path between these clocks, run the following command: report_timing -from [get_clocks rgmii_rxc] -to [get_clocks eth_125M_system_clock]
